The paper focuses on learning decentralized policies for multi-agent cooperative systems, which involves reinforcement learning and game theory concepts. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper also involves aspects of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), multi-agent systems (cs.MA), robotics (cs.RO), and game theory (cs.GT).
